{"tid":2157810,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蘋人誌：YouTube是我們反共戰場","createTime":"2020-08-15T09:35:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T09:35:57.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"158b1b261c985bf47fb7bcd128f8ecff3a0f4290","tid":2157810,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T09:35:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200815/B2GJYCXIOJGIXD2XJWU2NRMTTY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200815%2FB2GJYCXIOJGIXD2XJWU2NRMTTY%2F&d=kJyKEnCePQht%2Ftv3UrQe8bPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=49c18d47\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200815%2FB2GJYCXIOJGIXD2XJWU2NRMTTY%2F&h=0154cace\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200815/B2GJYCXIOJGIXD2XJWU2NRMTTY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n蘋人誌：YouTube是我們反共戰場<br />\n<br />\n樂樂法利（Lele Farley），一名熱愛中國文化的德州小子，曾在中國擔任非專業演員，。。。。。。。。。。。是準「洋五毛」；英提扎（Inty），一名嘗過中國種族歧視的新疆人，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：批評集中營 新疆網紅斷六親<br />\n<br />\n然而中國在總加速師習近平的領導下圖窮匕現，財大氣粗、無視人權的態度，激發起他倆反共決定。擁抱普世價值的兩人殊途同歸，成為海外戰線的YouTuber，也與港人連成一氣，全球圍中！"}]}